text: We order a lot of products,and we only show you the best products we buy
Today I'll be telling you about products that we personally bought and loved them
And i guarantee you'll like them as well. Out of 5 products there was one which did not work at all
Before i begin make sure to subscribe to the channel and turn on the notifications to get notified
Whenever we upload a video. I wanted a wireless charger as I'll be travelling in 2 days
You can also call it a magnetic charging pad
It comes with a cable so it's quite useful and portable It has a 2500mAh battery,so it can charge the phone upto 70-80%.
Our next product is a studio light. These are basically colourful hexagons and they come with stickers
These attach magnetically. With a tap you can turn on/off
The good thing is that you just have to attach one wire and all light up
They cost around Rs 2800 and all the links are in the description
These are great if you want something bright as your background
I wanted an alarm clock which was also multifunctional
The screen shows the time and you can also charge your phone on this
It comes with a 10W charger and it supports 10W wireless charging. It also has a light at the top
It will cost around Rs 2K
This laser projection keyboard is something you shouldn't buy
It is small, it projects from the screen. And it costed a whopping Rs 6500
As soon as i threw it, it started working
This was not scripted. As i threw it the projector started working
I think they should mention it in the manual saying make sure to drop before using
Our next product is also multifunctional,we normally order products which has many uses
It is a powerbank, also a lamp which allows colour customisation
The quality is really good. It is also a phone stand
It costs Rs 1800. And suprisingly the product we did not think works, worked very well
